title: The Feeling Themselves Power Rankings; Gronk Trade Talk and Woozy Bangers
itunes:title: The Feeling Themselves Power Rankings; Gronk Trade Talk and Woozy Bangers
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Steve Wyche & Colleen Wolfe get you up to speed with the latest news around the NFL including Gronkowski’s potential on returning to the league and playing for the Patriots (06:03), Josh Rosen’s former Coach Jim Mora on Sam Darnold fitting better with the Browns (13:41), the Raiders getting rid of Marquette King (21:30), and much more. The show concludes with The Feeling Themselves Power Rankings (32:11) where names like Sean Payton, John Gruden and Peyton Manning are thrown into the ring.
